p: The Gene Ontology (GO) terms and KEGG pathway enrichment analysis for the ASFV-interacting swine proteins or the ASFV infection-associated swine proteins were conducted with functions of enrichGO() and enrichKEGG() in the package “clusterProfiler” (version 3.6.0) ( Yu et al., 2012) in R (version 3.4.2). All the GO terms and KEGG pathways with adjusted p-values smaller than 0.01 were considered as significant enrichment ( Table S2).
